room_title: Escape room "Thwarted" by Exit Strategies in Redding
room_description:
As a member of an elite CIA advance team, your mission is to gather the necessary intelligence to prevent a planned terror attack. Your mission begins in a small street side market in southwestern India. Intel leads us to believe this market is a front for an especially brutal terrorist cell.
By successfully solving the cryptic puzzles and encoded messages, your team will uncover the date, time and place of their proposed attack. Work as a team, stay calm and remember your training.
